  "description": {
    "en": {
      "provenance": "imported",
      "value": "1.1:     Support the organization and conduct of national workshops to establish an intellectual and operational foundation for future policy analysis and dialogue;\r\n\r\n1.2: Preparation, signing and monitoring of LoAs with national policy research institutes;\r\n\r\n1.3: Undertake technical backstopping to provide support to national research institutes;\r\n\r\n2.1: Undertake an assessment of each country’s institutional and staff capacity in policy processes;\r\n\r\n2.2:Prepare and implement capacity-strengthening strategies and plans based on local needs, priorities and opportunities;\r\n\r\n2.3       Organize and conduct regional workshops to strengthen capacity for policy analysis among mid-level government officials and personnel of policy research institutes, farmer organizations and other civil society organizations\r\n\r\n2.4: Organize study tours for mid-level government officials of participating countries;\r\n\r\n3.1: Assist with the conduct of regional learning workshop(s) to provide participating countries with a forum to discuss innovative practices, cases of success or failure and lessons learned for stakeholders.\r\n\r\n3.2: Assist with the preparation of reports and dissemination of the results of these consultation and workshops."
    },
    "ne": null
  },
